title: What time is The Apprentice on tonight?
text:
What time is The Apprentice on tonight? By WMNdellis | Posted: October 14, 2015 9314698-low_res-the-apprentice-2015 What time is The Apprentice on tonight? X 
Copy link to paste in your message / 
Will you be tuning in to see the first episode of the latest series of The Apprentice tonight? 
It will see the candidates head to a fish market for their first task. 
To find out who’ll be the first to hear Lord Sugar snarl “You’re fired!”, tune in to BBC One at 9pm on 14 October. 
Episode two airs the following night, 15 October on BBC One at 9pm
